<Content>A pleasant surprise We stayed for four nights at this excellent hotel and were very impressed by the standard of accommodation. The food was some of the best that we have found in terms of quality, variety, and quantity. Staff were helpful and courteous. We could not ask for better, which added greatly to our enjoyment of our short holiday in Berlin. 
